        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks OB for his work on Schopenhauer [<hi rend="italic">Arthur Schopenhauer. Beitrag zu einer Dogmatik der Religionslosen</hi> (1877)]</p> 
            <p>and for his remarks on bees and clover. When CD spoke, last spring, of the few seeds produced by red clover, he supposed it was due to rarity of humble-bees.</p>
        </abstract>
